---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "@/images/navic_top.avif";
import buildingImage from "@/images/building.avif";
---

<section class="space-y-16 md:space-y-24">
  <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden sm:overflow-visible">
    <div class="relative sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Image Container -->
      <div
        class="relative w-full h-[60vh] sm:absolute sm:inset-y-0 sm:left-[40%] sm:w-[calc(10%+50vw)] sm:h-full"
      >
        <Image
          src={heroImage}
          alt="hero image"
          width={1600}
          height={900}
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 sm:hidden"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Container -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center sm:relative sm:inset-auto sm:h-auto sm:block sm:py-32 lg:py-56 sm:w-[40%]"
      >
        <h1
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-white sm:text-sky-900 leading-tight text-center sm:text-left px-4 sm:px-0 drop-shadow-md sm:drop-shadow-none sm:whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          人とのつながりを大切に。<br />
          様々な分野で新たな価値を生み出していく。
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12"
    >
      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-auto">
        <Image
          src={buildingImage}
          alt="building image"
          width={800}
          height={600}
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3
          class="text-center lg:text-left text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-sky-800 leading-tight"
        >
          常に先を見据えた<br />
          事業展開で<br />
          新たな未来を切り開く。
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
